title: Delay Your Gratification
itunes:title: Delay Your Gratification
description:
Episode 532 -  We live in a world of instant gratification. Everything we could ever want is at our fingertips. The problem with that is that success is not instant. In fact, success takes a long time, so in this episode I will talk about how to delay your gratification so that you can get the success you deserve.
